OL,3,CJersey to update 20th Century abortion
OL,4,Clegislation
OL,6,FJersey government has announced it
OL,7,Fwill resume work to update the
OL,8,Fisland's 27-year-old abortion laws
OL,9,Fafter it was halted in the summer due
OL,10,Fto a lack of resources.
OL,12,FAt a scrutiny panel on Friday 20
OL,13,FSeptember, the Chief Minister was
OL,14,Fasked why progress has stopped on
OL,15,Fdeveloping abortion law as well as
OL,16,Fother projects.
