OL,6,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham said: "We're
OL,7,Ftrying to find the balance that
OL,8,Faddresses the basics and we get those
OL,9,Fright first before we start putting on
OL,10,Fall the 'nice-to-haves' things."
OL,12,FITV News approached the Chief Minister
OL,13,Ffor comment, who said he was not
OL,14,Freferring directly to abortion
OL,15,Flegislation and was instead speaking
OL,16,Fabout government expenditure as a
OL,17,Fwhole.
