OL,6,FHowever, Jo Nash, founder of baby loss
OL,7,Fcharity Philip's Footprints, says: "I
OL,8,Fthink women's health issues are not a
OL,9,F'nice-to-have' - they are essential.
OL,11,F"I think it's really important that
OL,12,Fall of these things are considered -
OL,13,Fpeople's access to abortion should be
OL,14,Feasy and it should be free."
