OL,6,FTalking to ITV on Tuesday 24
OL,7,FSeptember, Deputy Tom Binet said the
OL,8,Fdecision to halt work didn't sit well
OL,9,Fwith him and confirmed that the
OL,10,Fgovernment has now found someone to
OL,11,Fwork up and submit policy documents to
OL,12,Fthe law department.
OL,14,FIn response, Chair of the Health and
OL,15,FSocial Security Panel, Deputy Louise
OL,16,FDoublet, said: "Five days ago the
OL,17,Fpanel were told it wasn't possible to
OL,18,Fcarry out the work.
