OL,6,F"We will be asking the Minister for
OL,7,Fevidence if this is indeed now
OL,8,Fpossible. The panel is minded to lodge
OL,9,Fan amendment to ensure that the work
OL,10,Fdoes definitely continue."
OL,12,FITV News wasn't told what specific
OL,13,Fchanges the new laws would make, but
OL,14,FDeputy Tom Binet said that work is
OL,15,Fprogressing and that there would be
OL,16,Ffewer barriers to women.
