OL,3,CJersey to update 20th Century abortion
OL,4,Clegislation
OL,6,FCurrent legislation won't allow a
OL,7,Fwoman to terminate her pregnancy after
OL,8,F12 weeks under most circumstances, a
OL,9,Fshorter period than Guernsey and the
OL,10,FUK which sits at 24 weeks.
OL,12,FJersey women who want to terminate
OL,13,Ftheir pregnancy also have to pay for
OL,14,Fthe procedure.JIn 2023, Jersey's
OL,15,Fgovernment launched a public
OL,16,Fconsultation on women's experiences of
OL,17,Fabortion on the island.
