OL,6,FOne respondent said: "There was no
OL,7,Femotional support afterwards. I went
OL,8,Fback to work the next day and cried in
OL,9,Fthe toilet."
OL,11,FAnother explained: "The doctor I saw
OL,12,Fin the hospital didn't sign me off
OL,13,Fwork afterwards, so I returned to work
OL,14,Fless than 18 hours after waking from
OL,15,Fgeneral anaesthetic, still bleeding."
OL,17,FITV News spoke to one of the women who
OL,18,Fshared their experience of termination
OL,19,Fin the consultation regarding the
OL,20,FChief Minister's comments.
