OL,6,FShe said: "The comment 'nice to have'
OL,7,Fmakes crucial women's care sound like
OL,8,Fan optional requirement and I'm
OL,9,Fdisappointed to hear that this is the
OL,10,FChief Minister's View.
OL,12,F"I would only hope that should their
OL,13,Ffamily ever require care in this area
OL,14,Ftheir experience would differ from my
OL,15,Fown and many others I know."
